documentation.text: This is a Zap contract to assist in the migration from the V1 Mero Pools to the new Mero Pools.

migrate(address).details: The user must have balance in the pool given, otherwise transaction will revert.
migrate(address).notice: Migrates a users balance from an old pool to a new pool.

params.oldPoolAddress_: The old pool to migrate for the user.

migrateAll(address[]).details: The user must have balance in all pools given, otherwise transaction will revert.
migrateAll(address[]).notice: Migrates all of a users balance from the old pools to the new pools.

params.oldPoolAddresses_: The list of old pools to migrate for the user.
